concept.title: SUPL Protocol Module
concept.shortdesc: The LBS subsystem contains a reference Network Protocol Module that supports the Open Mobile Alliance (OMA) SUPL V1.0 standard. This section contains documentation that describes the Symbian platform reference SUPL Protocol Module, its supporting components and APIs, its runtime behaviour and details about how it is configured by device creators.

conbody.p: Note: The SUPL Protocol Module is deprecated.
